00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:52.079
Evil cannot prevail over good.

00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:54.759
I still understand this principle.

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:57.800
As long as these hooligans

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:59.639
can be sanctioned by the law,

00:05:00.439 --> 00:05:03.560
then I will go to court to testify.

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:05.360
Would I be afraid of them?

